  "body": "Our multi-thread tests are failing very often. This issue is a tracker to aggregate the errors and hopefully figure out what's going on. I have no idea\r\n\r\nMay 20 2021 *Simulation multi thread multi node test altair epoch genesis* https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/pull/2541/checks?check_run_id=2629966394   \r\n```\r\nnode: ../binding.cc:545: Iterator::~Iterator(): Assertion `ended_' failed.\r\nAborted (core dumped)\r\nerror Command failed with exit code 134.\r\n```\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\nMay 20 2021 *Simulation multi thread multi node test altair epoch genesis* https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/pull/2540/checks?check_run_id=2629455362\r\n```\r\nSuccess: Terminating workers\r\nFATAL ERROR: v8::FromJust Maybe value is Nothing.\r\n 1: 0xa04200 node::Abort() [/opt/hostedtoolcache/node/14.16.0/x64/bin/node]\r\n 2: 0x94e4e9 node::FatalError(char const*, char const*) [/opt/hostedtoolcache/node/14.16.0/x64/bin/node]\r\n 3: 0xb794aa v8::Utils::ReportApiFailure(char const*, char const*) [/opt/hostedtoolcache/node/14.16.0/x64/bin/node]\r\n 4: 0xab5e65 node::worker::Worker::JoinThread() [/opt/hostedtoolcache/node/14.16.0/x64/bin/node]\r\n 5: 0x9a4298 node::Environment::RunAndClearNativeImmediates(bool) [/opt/hostedtoolcache/node/14.16.0/x64/bin/node]\r\n 6: 0x137bb06  [/opt/hostedtoolcache/node/14.16.0/x64/bin/node]\r\n 7: 0x138e5e5  [/opt/hostedtoolcache/node/14.16.0/x64/bin/node]\r\n 8: 0x137c438 uv_run [/opt/hostedtoolcache/node/14.16.0/x64/bin/node]\r\n 9: 0xabc4a3 node::worker::Worker::Run() [/opt/hostedtoolcache/node/14.16.0/x64/bin/node]\r\n10: 0xabcf28  [/opt/hostedtoolcache/node/14.16.0/x64/bin/node]\r\n11: 0x7f8b1276c609  [/lib/x86_64-linux-gnu/libpthread.so.0]\r\n12: 0x7f8b12693293 clone [/lib/x86_64-linux-gnu/libc.so.6]\r\nAborted (core dumped)\r\nerror Command failed with exit code 134.\r\n```\r\n```\r\nnode: ../binding.cc:545: Iterator::~Iterator(): Assertion `ended_' failed.\r\nAborted (core dumped)\r\nerror Command failed with exit code 134.\r\n```\r\n```\r\nSuccess: Terminating workers\r\nSegmentation fault (core dumped)\r\nerror Command failed with exit code 139.\r\n```\r\nMay 26 2021\r\n```\r\nnode: ../binding.cc:545: Iterator::~Iterator(): Assertion `ended_' failed.\r\n~/Code/lodestar$ find node_modules -name binding.cc\r\nnode_modules/leveldown/binding.cc\r\nnode_modules/snappy/src/binding.cc\r\n```",
